name: HealthHarbor
overview: HealthHarbor, LLC, is a web-based resource offering healthcare consumers with interactive tools, content, and community, allowing them to become smarter consumers of their healthcare. It provides online tools helping consumers locate affordable care alternatives, vaccines, discounted prescription drugs, affordable health plans, and how to best use health coverage. It also provides content helping people save money on healthcare, understand their health coverage, get the most from flexible spending accounts and open enrollment, and navigate the healthcare system more effectively. The company was founded in 2008 and is based in Minneapolis, MN.
